535
00:33:44,280 --> 00:33:45,800
No, I'm going alone.

536
00:33:46,560 --> 00:33:47,560
I should get going.

537
00:33:48,600 --> 00:33:51,120
When she calls again,
tell her you want to meet immediately.

538
00:33:51,200 --> 00:33:52,360
And call me.

539
00:33:58,640 --> 00:34:00,280
This is so annoying.

540
00:34:05,360 --> 00:34:09,199
How's work? Is it bearable?

541
00:34:10,320 --> 00:34:12,360
Yes, I'm giving it my best.

542
00:34:13,560 --> 00:34:14,600
I'm glad to hear that.

543
00:34:14,960 --> 00:34:18,000
I hope you will improve.
I'm rooting for you.

544
00:34:18,400 --> 00:34:21,360
Of course.
I need to help this station flourish

545
00:34:21,440 --> 00:34:23,679
in order for them to pay me back.

546
00:34:23,960 --> 00:34:26,080
I'm giving it my best.

547
00:34:26,920 --> 00:34:29,040
Well... All right.

548
00:34:29,960 --> 00:34:31,000
Listen.

549
00:34:32,760 --> 00:34:36,040
You and Dong-chan don't get along, do you?

550
00:34:36,679 --> 00:34:37,679
Not really.

551
00:34:38,120 --> 00:34:42,120
I'll let you pick the director
you'd like to work with.

552
00:34:42,320 --> 00:34:43,440
Just say the name.

553
00:34:44,239 --> 00:34:45,280
No, thank you.

554
00:34:47,040 --> 00:34:50,800
I think he's the best director out there.

555
00:34:51,520 --> 00:34:53,679
Ever since he did "Infinite Experiment
Paradise" 20 years ago,

556
00:34:53,760 --> 00:34:56,239
I have admired his passion and competence.

557
00:34:57,800 --> 00:34:59,640
I want to learn from him.

558
00:35:00,440 --> 00:35:02,960
You want to keep working with him
even though you guys fight so much?

559
00:35:03,200 --> 00:35:06,240
Yes.
It's not like he'll become my husband.

560
00:35:08,560 --> 00:35:10,120
He's an excellent worker,
and that's enough.

561
00:35:11,280 --> 00:35:12,680
Why do you want to keep her by your side

562
00:35:12,840 --> 00:35:14,880
when you guys fight so often?

563
00:35:15,360 --> 00:35:17,520
