to become a director.

564
00:35:17,600 --> 00:35:20,720
She's got talent.
She has good sense and imagination.

565
00:35:21,040 --> 00:35:24,120
She seems promising
as long as she's guided well.

566
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:27,000
But you two have an awful relationship.

567
00:35:27,840 --> 00:35:29,960
I don't work with people
because I like them.

568
00:35:30,120 --> 00:35:32,120
-It's just work.
-You're right about that.

569
00:35:34,640 --> 00:35:35,640
Hey.

570
00:35:36,200 --> 00:35:39,520
