if they find out about her age.

575
00:35:51,360 --> 00:35:53,960
All right. I'll take care of that.

576
00:35:54,040 --> 00:35:55,040
Thanks.

577
00:35:56,200 --> 00:35:57,560
Do take care of her.

578
00:35:58,040 --> 00:36:00,960
She may seem strong,

579
00:36:02,120 --> 00:36:03,920
but she's sensitive like me.

580
00:36:10,720 --> 00:36:14,400
Ta-da. I'm in the hallway
of TBO Broadcasting Station

581
00:36:14,480 --> 00:36:16,760
where my best friend works.

582
00:36:16,840 --> 00:36:18,120
If you look behind me,

583
00:36:18,200 --> 00:36:21,280
