584
00:36:21,640 --> 00:36:22,680
And...

585
00:36:28,840 --> 00:36:30,040
Did you see him?

586
00:36:30,120 --> 00:36:33,640
The renowned cryonics man, Ma Dong-chan,

587
00:36:33,720 --> 00:36:35,040
just entered the bathroom.

588
00:36:35,560 --> 00:36:38,320
I can't believe I'll be seeing him
in person! Let's go inside.

589
00:36:40,440 --> 00:36:42,520
-Yu-ja!
-Mi-ran!

590
00:36:46,760 --> 00:36:48,120
Let's pray first.

591
